  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“4 Rush Together\" is a lighthearted and humorous cooperative level-clearing game. You and your friends will be tied together by a rope, adventuring happily through creatively designed levels. You can invite up to three friends for local multiplayer or online co-op play. What are you waiting for? Start a hilarious journey with your friends that will have you laughing until your stomach hurts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【The game is a multiplayer cooperative experience, so playing in single-player mode might feel less challenging and reduce the fun. However, once you team up with friends, the joy doubles, the laughter doubles, but so does the difficulty! So gather your friends and enjoy some hilarious rush together!】</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rich and Fun Level Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level has unique gameplay awaiting the challenge of you and your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a01c86e4884e9f97bbb2c3d97a138595.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a01c86e4884e9f97bbb2c3d97a138595.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a01c86e4884e9f97bbb2c3d97a138595.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/0376b58987711ba85ff6d14ebed465b5.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/0376b58987711ba85ff6d14ebed465b5.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/0376b58987711ba85ff6d14ebed465b5.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Competitive and Cooperative Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features two play modes: Competitive Mode and Cooperative Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Competitive Mode:</strong> In this mode, players are not constrained by ropes. You and your friends will compete to see who reaches the finish line first.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/f2fddfdb22390bdfa11d8173a51c664d.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/f2fddfdb22390bdfa11d8173a51c664d.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/f2fddfdb22390bdfa11d8173a51c664d.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/ce2023e48743a74db51602c212072bb6.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/ce2023e48743a74db51602c212072bb6.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/ce2023e48743a74db51602c212072bb6.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cooperative Mode:</strong> You and your friends will be connected by a rope and need to work seamlessly together to reach the finish line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/e728da81403f12a9a1897aa2b7d81bb8.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/e728da81403f12a9a1897aa2b7d81bb8.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/e728da81403f12a9a1897aa2b7d81bb8.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a7626ddd44d877747d417978e9fd3c81.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a7626ddd44d877747d417978e9fd3c81.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a7626ddd44d877747d417978e9fd3c81.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hilarious Level Mechanisms</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game features a variety of amusing mechanisms and traps that will bring a hilarious gaming experience.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/47a03f6e76d1323ec8db7d4f7680112a.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/47a03f6e76d1323ec8db7d4f7680112a.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/47a03f6e76d1323ec8db7d4f7680112a.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/95bef119cee91b36cc82cf2aa0d6c535.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/95bef119cee91b36cc82cf2aa0d6c535.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/95bef119cee91b36cc82cf2aa0d6c535.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Single or Multiplayer Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports playing alone locally or cooperating with friends on the same screen. You can also play online remotely with friends, supporting up to 4 players to clear levels together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/5f6fe6ee8aa51914cacd3218a7887ca9.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/5f6fe6ee8aa51914cacd3218a7887ca9.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/5f6fe6ee8aa51914cacd3218a7887ca9.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leaderboard</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The leaderboard records players' level completion times and displays how long they took to clear levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/75fe6f061a0672367c858e0c85adc5d0.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/75fe6f061a0672367c858e0c85adc5d0.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/75fe6f061a0672367c858e0c85adc5d0.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/9d9ca2614b356728a74b2619d6a3dadb.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/9d9ca2614b356728a74b2619d6a3dadb.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/9d9ca2614b356728a74b2619d6a3dadb.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/6c6c5183d9fea2a954734ba3b0b8d979.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/6c6c5183d9fea2a954734ba3b0b8d979.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/6c6c5183d9fea2a954734ba3b0b8d979.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“4 Rush Together\" is a lighthearted and humorous cooperative level-clearing game. You and your friends will be tied together by a rope, adventuring happily through creatively designed levels. You can invite up to three friends for local multiplayer or online co-op play. What are you waiting for? Start a hilarious journey with your friends that will have you laughing until your stomach hurts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【The game is a multiplayer cooperative experience, so playing in single-player mode might feel less challenging and reduce the fun. However, once you team up with friends, the joy doubles, the laughter doubles, but so does the difficulty! So gather your friends and enjoy some hilarious rush together!】</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rich and Fun Level Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level has unique gameplay awaiting the challenge of you and your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a01c86e4884e9f97bbb2c3d97a138595.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a01c86e4884e9f97bbb2c3d97a138595.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a01c86e4884e9f97bbb2c3d97a138595.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/0376b58987711ba85ff6d14ebed465b5.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/0376b58987711ba85ff6d14ebed465b5.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/0376b58987711ba85ff6d14ebed465b5.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Competitive and Cooperative Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features two play modes: Competitive Mode and Cooperative Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Competitive Mode:</strong> In this mode, players are not constrained by ropes. You and your friends will compete to see who reaches the finish line first.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/f2fddfdb22390bdfa11d8173a51c664d.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/f2fddfdb22390bdfa11d8173a51c664d.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/f2fddfdb22390bdfa11d8173a51c664d.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/ce2023e48743a74db51602c212072bb6.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/ce2023e48743a74db51602c212072bb6.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/ce2023e48743a74db51602c212072bb6.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cooperative Mode:</strong> You and your friends will be connected by a rope and need to work seamlessly together to reach the finish line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/e728da81403f12a9a1897aa2b7d81bb8.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/e728da81403f12a9a1897aa2b7d81bb8.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/e728da81403f12a9a1897aa2b7d81bb8.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a7626ddd44d877747d417978e9fd3c81.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a7626ddd44d877747d417978e9fd3c81.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/a7626ddd44d877747d417978e9fd3c81.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hilarious Level Mechanisms</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game features a variety of amusing mechanisms and traps that will bring a hilarious gaming experience.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/47a03f6e76d1323ec8db7d4f7680112a.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/47a03f6e76d1323ec8db7d4f7680112a.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/47a03f6e76d1323ec8db7d4f7680112a.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/95bef119cee91b36cc82cf2aa0d6c535.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/95bef119cee91b36cc82cf2aa0d6c535.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/95bef119cee91b36cc82cf2aa0d6c535.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Single or Multiplayer Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports playing alone locally or cooperating with friends on the same screen. You can also play online remotely with friends, supporting up to 4 players to clear levels together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/5f6fe6ee8aa51914cacd3218a7887ca9.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/5f6fe6ee8aa51914cacd3218a7887ca9.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/5f6fe6ee8aa51914cacd3218a7887ca9.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leaderboard</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The leaderboard records players' level completion times and displays how long they took to clear levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/75fe6f061a0672367c858e0c85adc5d0.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/75fe6f061a0672367c858e0c85adc5d0.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/75fe6f061a0672367c858e0c85adc5d0.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/9d9ca2614b356728a74b2619d6a3dadb.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/9d9ca2614b356728a74b2619d6a3dadb.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/9d9ca2614b356728a74b2619d6a3dadb.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/6c6c5183d9fea2a954734ba3b0b8d979.poster.avif?t=1770643442\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/6c6c5183d9fea2a954734ba3b0b8d979.webm?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697170/extras/6c6c5183d9fea2a954734ba3b0b8d979.mp4?t=1770643442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>